---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sports Digital Network | Arena & Golf Course Advertising in Canada"
  description="Canada's premium sports venue advertising network. Reach 3.6M weekly visitors across 100+ arenas and golf courses. 90+ minutes of captive attention per visit."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Your audience is already here. They stay for 90 minutes.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">Every week, 3.6 million Canadians walk into community arenas, recreation centres, and golf courses — and they don't leave for an hour and a half. They watch their kids play hockey. They wait for a tee time. They cheer from the stands. And while they're there, they see your message on our screens.</p>
      <p>Sports Digital Network operates Canada's largest digital out-of-home network in community sports venues. Our 65-inch 4K screens deliver full-screen advertising to a captive, affluent audience across 100+ facilities from Vancouver to Halifax.</p>
      <p class="hero-tagline">No scrolling past. No skipping. No ad blockers. Just real people, in real places, with real time to notice your brand.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-ways">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Two ways we help</h2>
      <div class="two-ways-grid">
        <div class="way-card">
          <h3>For advertisers</h3>
          <p>Reach families, sports enthusiasts, and high-income households in the places where they spend their time — not where they scroll past your ad in 0.4 seconds.</p>
          <p>Whether you're a national brand looking for coast-to-coast coverage or a local business targeting a single community, our network puts your message in front of engaged audiences with the longest dwell times in out-of-home advertising.</p>
          <a href="/advertisers/" class="btn btn-primary">Explore advertising options</a>
        </div>
        <div class="way-card">
          <h3>For venue owners</h3>
          <p>Turn your arena lobbies, golf clubhouses, and recreation centre hallways into revenue streams — without lifting a finger. SDN installs the screens, manages the content, sells the advertising, and sends you a cheque every month.</p>
          <a href="/venues/" class="btn btn-primary">Become a venue partner</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The numbers that matter</h2>
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">premium venues across Canada</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">3.6M</span>
          <span class="stat-label">weekly visitors</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">35M</span>
          <span class="stat-label">weekly impressions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">90+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">minutes average dwell time</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">35%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">higher household income than median</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why community venues outperform every other medium</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Captive attention, not borrowed glances</h3>
          <p>A traditional billboard gets six seconds. A digital banner ad gets ignored. Community venues deliver 90+ minutes of repeated exposure to an audience that chose to be there and has nowhere else to look.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Context that builds trust</h3>
          <p>Your ad appears alongside hockey games, swimming lessons, and Saturday morning figure skating. That's a brand-safe, family-friendly environment that no programmatic buy can guarantee.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Precision that scales</h3>
          <p>Target a single arena in Barrie or light up every major market in Canada. Our network gives you the hyperlocal reach of community advertising with the scale of a national DOOH platform.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partners-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our network partners</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">SDN operates screens in partnership with Canada's leading venue operators:</p>
      <div class="partners-list">
        <div class="partner">
          <strong>ClubLink</strong> — Canada's largest owner of private golf courses (24 Ontario locations)
        </div>
        <div class="partner">
          <strong>Canlan Sports</strong> — Canada's largest operator of private arenas
        </div>
        <div class="partner">
          <strong>Nustadia Recreation</strong> — Canada's largest operator of community arena facilities
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="partners-note">95% of our venues are multi-pad and multi-sport facilities — the biggest, busiest buildings in their communities.</p>
      <a href="/network/locations/" class="btn btn-secondary">See all locations</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">1</span>
          <h3>Choose your audience</h3>
          <p>Pick specific venues, cities, or go national. Target hockey parents, golfers, or multi-sport families.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">2</span>
          <h3>We handle the creative</h3>
          <p>Our team designs your ad for maximum impact on large-format screens. Or supply your own — we accept static and video.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <h3>Your ad goes live</h3>
          <p>Full-screen placements run alongside sports content, weather, and community information. No clutter. No competition for attention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">4</span>
          <h3>See your results</h3>
          <p>Track impressions, reach, and campaign performance through our reporting dashboard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to put your brand where Canadians spend their time?</h2>
    <p>Whether you want to advertise to millions of sports families or generate revenue from your facility's foot traffic, we'd like to hear from you.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-white">Request a proposal</a>
      <a href="/resources/media-kit/" class="btn-outline">Download our media kit</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--dark) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .hero-lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.2rem !important;
    opacity: 1 !important;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .two-ways {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .two-ways h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .two-ways-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .way-card {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .way-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .way-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .way-card .btn {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .stats-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .stats-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--blue);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .why-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .why-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .why-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .why-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .why-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .partners-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .partners-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .partners-list {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .partner {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200, #e9ecef);
  }
  .partner:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .partners-note {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .partners-section .btn {
    display: block;
    width: fit-content;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .how-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .how-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .step-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .step h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .step p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--white);
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .two-ways-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
